sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin
    participant FE as Frontend Port 3001
    participant BE as Backend Port 3000
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant BC as CredentialRegistry
    participant V as Public Verifier

    Admin->>FE: Upload Excel CSV
    FE->>BE: POST file-upload batch
    BE->>BE: Compute keccak256 data_hash
    BE->>DB: Save certificates status ISSUED

    Admin->>FE: Issue to Blockchain
    FE->>BE: POST issue-to-blockchain
    BE->>DB: Load certs and university DID
    BE->>BC: issueCredentials hashes and DIDs
    BC-->>BE: Transaction hash
    BE->>DB: Update status VERIFIED

    V->>FE: Open verify page or scan QR
    FE->>BE: GET verification certificate_id
    BE->>DB: Load certificate student university
    BE->>BE: Recompute hash match stored hash
    BE->>BC: getCredential data_hash
    BC-->>BE: issuerDid blockTime isRevoked exists
    BE-->>FE: Valid if all three gates pass
